{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozOpaque\"><code>mozOpaque</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>captureStream()</code></a></li><li><em><code>getContext()</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozFetchAsStream\"><code>mozFetchAsStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>toDataURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextlost_event\"><code>webglcontextlost</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p class=\"summary\">Metoda&nbsp;<strong><code>HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()</code></strong>&nbsp;zwraca kontekst pola&nbsp;roboczego <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, lub&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a> jeśli&nbsp;&nbsp;identyfikator kontekstu nie jest wspierany.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>ctx</em> = <em>canvas</em>.getContext(<em>contextType</em>);\nvar <em>ctx</em> = <em>canvas</em>.getContext(<em>contextType</em>, <em>contextAttributes</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"contexttype\"><code><em>contextType</em></code></dt>\n <dd>Jest nim&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zawierający identyfikator kontekstu pola roboczego powiązanego z&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Możliwe wartości to:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>\"2d\"</code>,&nbsp; tworzy&nbsp;obiekt <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> reprezentujący dwuwymiarowy kontekst renderowania.</li>\n  <li><code>\"webgl\"</code> (lub&nbsp;<code>\"experimental-webgl\"</code>), tworzy obiekt <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> reprezentujący trójwymiarowy kontekst renderowania. Ten kontekst&nbsp;dostępny jest tylko w przeglądarkach&nbsp;w których zaimplementowana&nbsp;jest wersja 1 WebGL (OpenGL ES 2.0).</li>\n  <li><code>\"webgl2\"</code>&nbsp;tworzy obiekt&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> reprezentujący trójwymiarowy kontekst renderowania. Ten kontekst&nbsp;dostępny jest tylko w przeglądarkach&nbsp;w których zaimplementowana&nbsp;jest wersja 2&nbsp;WebGL (OpenGL ES 3.0). <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n  <li><code>\"bitmaprenderer\"</code> tworzy <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, który zapewnia możliwość zastąpenia treści&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;na podaną <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n </ul>\n\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n <p><strong>Nota</strong>: Identyfikator&nbsp;\"<code>experimental-webgl</code>\"&nbsp;jest używany przy nowych wdrożeniach WebGL. Wdrożenia te nie uzyskały zgodności z pakietem testowym lub sterowniki graficzne platformy nie są jeszcze stabilne. <a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Grupa Khronos </a>certyfikuje wdrożenia WebGL zgodnie z <a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/sdk/tests/CONFORMANCE_RULES.txt\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">regułami zgodności</a>.</p>\n </div>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"contextattributes\"><code><em>contextAttributes</em></code></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Można użyć kilku własności kontekstu przy tworzeniu kontekstu renderowania, dla przykładu:&nbsp;</p>\n\n <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> gl <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'webgl'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">antialias</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">depth</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n </dd>\n <dd>Własności kontekstu 2d:\n <ul>\n  <li><strong><code>alpha</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujacy czy canvas zawiera kanał alpha. Jeśli ustawione na&nbsp;<code>false</code>, przeglądarka wie, że tło zawsze jest nieprzeźroczyste, co może przyspieszyć rysowanie przeźroczystych treści i obrazków.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> (Gecko only) <strong><code>willReadFrequently</code></strong>:&nbsp;Boolean wskazujący czy wiele operacji&nbsp;<code>read-back</code>&nbsp;zostało zaplanowanych. Spowoduje wymuszenie użycia oprogramowania (zamiast przyśpieszenia sprzętowego) 2D canvas i może pomóc w oszczędności pamięci przy częstym wywoływaniu&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getImageData\"><code>getImageData()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Opcja ta jest dostepna tylko jeśli flaga&nbsp;<code>gfx.canvas.willReadFrequently.enable</code>&nbsp;jest ustawiona na <code>true</code>&nbsp;(która, domyślnie, dotyczy tylko B2G/Firefox OS).</li>\n  <li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> (Blink only) <strong><code>storage</code></strong>: String wskazujacy jaka pamięć jest używana (domyślnie jest to \"stała\" ).</li>\n </ul>\n Własności kontekstu WebGL:\n\n <ul>\n  <li><strong><code>alpha</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujacy czy canvas zawiera bufor alpha.</li>\n  <li><strong><code>depth</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujący czy bufor rysunku posiada bufor głębi o wartości co przynajmniej 16 bitów.</li>\n  <li><strong><code>stencil</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujący&nbsp;czy bufor rysunku posiada bufor matrycy o wartości przynajmniej 8 bitów.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li><strong><code>antialias</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujący czy używany ma być <code>anti-aliasing.</code></li>\n  <li><strong><code>premultipliedAlpha</code></strong>: Boolean wskazujący czy projektant strony założył, że&nbsp;&nbsp;bufor rysunku zawiera kolory ze wstepnie pomnożoną alfą.</li>\n  <li><strong><code>preserveDrawingBuffer</code></strong>: Jeśli ustawiona na&nbsp;<code>true</code>, bufory nie zostaną wyczyszczone i zachowają swoje wartości, dopóki nie zostaną wyczyszczone lub nadpisane przez autora.</li>\n  <li><code><strong>failIfMajorPerformanceCaveat</strong></code>: Boolean wskazujący czy kontekst będzie tworzony, jeśli wydajność systemu jest niska.</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wartości_zwrotne","title":"Wartości zwrotne","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>RenderingContext</code></a> jest też</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> dla&nbsp;<code>\"2d\"</code>,</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> dla&nbsp;<code>\"webgl\"</code> i&nbsp;<code>\"experimental-webgl\"</code>,</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> dla&nbsp;<code>\"webgl2\"</code>&nbsp;lub</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> dla&nbsp;<code>\"bitmaprenderer\"</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Jeśli&nbsp;<em><code>contextType</code></em>&nbsp;nie może dopasować możliwych kontekstów rysowania,&nbsp;<code><em>null</em></code>&nbsp;zostanie zwrócony.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wykorzystując element <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Kontekst&nbsp;<code>2d</code>&nbsp;uzyskać można za pomocą kodu:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// CanvasRenderingContext2D { ... }</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Tworzy to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\">kontekst renderowania 2D</a>, po którym można rysować.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-canvas-getcontext\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.getContext' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Brak zmian od ostatniego snapshota, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML5' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/scripting-1.html#dom-canvas-getcontext\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.getContext' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/scripting-1.html#dom-canvas-getcontext\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.getContext' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Snapshot <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a> zawiera początkową definicje.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Zgodność przeglądarek","id":"zgodność_przeglądarek","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.getContext","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_też","title":"Zobacz też","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Interfejs definiujacy element, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a>.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas/getContext\"><code>OffscreenCanvas.getContext()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li>Dostępne konteksty renderowania: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL2RenderingContext\"><code>WebGL2RenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> i&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"składnia"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przykłady"},{"text":"Specyfikacja","id":"specyfikacja"},{"text":"Zgodność przeglądarek","id":"zgodność_przeglądarek"},{"text":"Zobacz też","id":"zobacz_też"}],"summary":"Metoda HTMLCanvasElement.getContext() zwraca kontekst pola roboczego <canvas> (en-US), lub null jeśli  identyfikator kontekstu nie jest wspierany.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/getcontext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/getcontext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement","title":"HTMLCanvasElement"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext","title":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLCanvasElement.getContext() - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}